Veusz basic installation procedure
----------------------------------

The code just runs in its current directory at the moment.
It needs a distutils / installation script

Requirements:
 python 2.3      http://www.python.org/
 PyQt            http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/pyqt/
 Numarray        http://www.stsci.edu/resources/software_hardware/numarray


(PyQt requres
 QT              http://www.trolltech.com/products/qt/
 SIP             http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/sip/   )

Install the above requirements.

Run the program using

./veusz.py

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
